Download TIGER shapes for American Indian / Alaska Native / Native Hawaiian Areas

Source: R/ai_an_nh_areas.R
tt_ai_an_nh_areas.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for American Indian / Alaska Native / Native Hawaiian Areas

Usage

tt_ai_an_nh_areas(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2021 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try({tt_ai_an_nh_areas()})
